title: [Gyldemar Forest, Cliff Base]
description: Gentle winds blow along the cliffs, sending pebbles skipping downward.  A few small trees have grown out from the cliffside, their thin limbs gently rustling in the wind.
Gentle winds blow along the cliffs, sending pebbles skipping downward.  A few small trees have grown out from the dark cliffside, their thin limbs gently rustling in the wind.
